name: Tribal Mixed Metal Earrings - Handmade Modern Tribal Jewelry
description:
These handmade mixed metal earrings have a modern tribal vibe. They feature hand fabricated sterling silver and copper shapes. I designed the shapes, sawed them out of metal sheet, and then hand stamped and hammered the tribal pattern into the metal. They were oxidized, buffed and polished to bring out the texture's detail.

 The earrings measure 2-3/4” in length and 1-1/8” in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of approx. 3" from the top of the sterling silver ear wires. They are signed on the back with my initials and the sterling stamp.

These earrings are unique - and will make a bold and striking statement!

name: Hammered Sterling Silver Cuff Bracelet
description:
This sterling silver cuff bracelet has a rustic, organic style and can be worn everyday. It features a unique hammered and stamped texture. I formed the bracelet - by hand - out of solid sterling silver sheet; and hammered and stamped the metal to create the texture. The silver was oxidized, buffed and hand polished to bring out the deep, rich detail.

The cuff measures 5/8” in width and 5-3/4” in length - along with a 1” opening - for a total circumference of 6-3/4”. It was hand formed from heavy gauge solid sterling silver……but can be *slightly* adjusted by *gently* squeezing or stretching the sides to conform to your individual wrist. It is signed on the back with my initials and the sterling stamp. All of the edges were hand filed and sanded until ultra-smooth - to ensure a comfortable wear against the skin. 

This cuff is perfect for those who prefer a narrow width bracelet. It can also be worn stacked on your wrist along with other cuff bracelets, for a layered effect.

name: Hammered Sterling Silver Dangle Earrings with Natural Turquoise
description:
Hand hammered sterling silver earrings with stacks of earthy turquoise. These handmade earrings have a modern and tribal flair -- and will make a bold and striking statement. I created the shapes out of sterling silver sheet; hammered the metal to create an earthy, organic texture - and then gave it a charcoal patina to bring out the detail. Stacks of natural turquoise were added to swing above the silver shapes. This turquoise is a lovely shade of bluish-green, and has a subtle matrix of brownish-black veining.

The earrings measure approx. 1-3/4” in length and 1-3/8” in width (at widest point), and will hang for a total length of approx. 2" from the top of the sterling silver ear wires. They are signed on the back with my initials and the sterling stamp.

name: Modern Sterling Silver Cuff Bracelet with Hand Stamped Design
description:
This sterling silver cuff is unique, modern and stylish - and versatile enough to be worn everyday. 

I formed this cuff out of heavy, 18 gauge sterling sheet for strength and durability. The texture was created by lightly hammering and hand stamping the metal. Each little line and dot you see takes one blow with a hammer and stamping tool to create the detailed pattern. All of the edges were hand filed and sanded until ultra-smooth - to ensure a comfortable wear against the skin. The silver was given a charcoal patina, and then buffed and polished to bring out the detail.

It measures 1-1/4” in width and 5-3/4” in length - along with a 1-1/4” opening in the back - for a total circumference of 7". It is signed on the back with my initials and the sterling stamp.

This cuff has a substantial weight to it - but can be *slightly* adjusted by *gently* squeezing or stretching the sides to conform to your individual wrist.  It should fit an average wrist that measures between 6-7 inches.

name: Large Sterling Silver Earrings with Turquoise Nuggets
description:
These large sterling silver earrings feature gorgeous turquoise nuggets, along with hand fabricated sterling silver shapes. I sawed the shapes out of solid sterling silver sheet, and then hammered them repeatedly to create the intricate texture. The silver was given a charcoal patina, and then buffed and polished to bring out the rich detail. Gorgeous, natural turquoise nuggets were added to complete the organic look. This turquoise has beautiful hues of blue and green, along with a natural matrix of copper veining.

The earrings measure 3” in length and 7/8” in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of 3-1/4” from the top of the sterling silver ear wires. They are signed on the back with my initials and the sterling stamp.  

These earrings have a modern, contemporary - yet tribal type of flair - and will make a bold and striking statement.

name: Large Hammered Gold Moon Dangle Earrings
description:
Large gold brass moon earrings with a lovely, hammered organic texture. These handmade earrings remind me of a large, luminous gold moon. They feature a dangling double circle design, which I created out of solid gold brass sheet. I hammered and rippled the metal for an organic texture - and then oxidized it to bring out the rustic highlights. The end result has the look of aged gold. These earrings have an "Old World" feel to them .... like something that could have been unearthed in an archeological dig. 

The measure 2-1/2" in length and 1-1/2" in width (at widest point) and will hang for a total length of approx. 2-3/4" from the top of the yellow bronze ear wires.

These earrings have a modern, organic appeal - and can be worn with a variety of outfits - dressed up or down.

name: Hammered Sterling Silver Earrings with Dangling Black Onyx Gemstones - Egyptian Inspired Jewelry
description:
Long and luxe, black onyx gemstones were combined with handcrafted sterling silver to create these exotic Egyptian inspired earrings. I created the earrings out of solid sterling silver sheet, and hammered the metal for an earthy, primal texture. The silver was given a charcoal patina, and then buffed and polished to bring out the detail. Stunning black onyx gemstones were added to dangle from the bottom.

These earrings have an exotic “Old World” and ancient Egyptian type of flair -- and will make a bold and unique statement.

They measure 2-1/4” in length and 1-1/8” in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of approx. 2-5/8" from the top of the sterling silver ear wires. The earrings are signed on the back with my initials and the sterling stamp.

name: Sterling Silver Leaf Earrings with Hand Stamped Design - Modern Contemporary Nature Jewelry
description:
Handmade sterling silver leaf earrings with an intricate hand stamped design. These earrings have a modern, contemporary and simplistic appeal. 

I created the earrings out of solid sterling silver sheet. I hand stamped the intricate leaf pattern into the metal with my favorite stamping tool, which was given to me by my father. Every mark you see takes one blow with a hammer and a stamping tool to create this intricate design. I added "brush strokes" to the surface for additional visual interest, and then gave the metal a charcoal patina to bring out the rich detail.

The earrings measure 2-1/8” in length and 7/8” in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of approx. 2-1/2”  from the top of the sterling silver ear wires. They are signed on the back with my initials and the sterling stamp. 

I can create these earrings in any size you wish. If you would like a specific size ..... please contact me and we can arrange to have a custom pair made exclusively for you!

name: Handmade Egyptian Inspired Sterling Silver Earrings with Black Jasper Gemstones
description:
These bold and striking earrings were inspired by "Old World" designs and have an exotic, ancient Egyptian flair. I designed the earring shapes; sawed them out of solid sterling silver sheet; and hammered and stamped a unique primal texture into the metal. The silver was given a charcoal patina and then buffed and polished to bring out the detail. Gorgeous black jasper gemstones were wrapped in sterling silver wire and added to dangle from the bottom. These stones are a beautiful teardrop shape and have a deep opaque black hue and a semi-matte finish.

The earrings measure approx. 2-1/8” in length and 1-1/4” in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of 2-1/2” from the top of the sterling silver ear wires. They are signed on the back with my initials and the sterling stamp.

name: Hammered Sterling Silver Earrings with Carnelian Gemstones
description:
These handmade earrings have an exotic, "Old World" and bohemian tribal vibe. They feature stunning carnelian gemstones that have been carved into unique, fan-shaped "slices". They have a deep, rich burnt-orange hue and a lovely translucent luster. Handmade sterling silver circles were added to dangle from the bottom. The silver was hammered; a few holes were added for a rustic effect; and then the metal was given a charcoal patina to bring out the detail.

The earrings measure 2-1/4” in length and 1-1/2” in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of 2-5/8" from the top of the sterling silver ear wires. The earrings are signed on the back with my initials and the sterling stamp.

name: Contemporary Mixed Metal Earrings with Hammered Organic Texture
description:
Handmade mixed metal earrings with a modern and contemporary aesthetic. These unique earrings were made by hand and are perfect for everyday wear. I designed the contemporary shapes and then sawed them out of solid gold brass sheet. I hammered the metal to create a rich, organic texture and then oxidized it to bring out the detail. The brass shapes were wrapped with abstract twists of nickel silver wire for additional visual interest.

These earrings are very versatile and can be worn with a variety of outfits and styles - dressed up or down. They are also lightweight and comfortable to wear.

The earrings measure approx. 1-1/2” in length and 1 in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of 1-7/8” from the top of my handmade sterling silver ear wires. The earrings are signed on the back with my initials.

name: Gold Brass Earrings with Dangling Black Tourmaline Raw Gemstones
description:
Hammered gold brass earrings with raw black tourmaline gemstones. These long and sexy gold brass earrings have a sophisticated, edgy and modern appeal. I created the shapes out of solid gold brass sheet, filed all of the edges until ultra smooth, and then hammered the metal for texture. The brass shapes were wrapped in blackened nickel silver wire for a dramatic effect - and the black tourmaline stones were added to dangle from the bottom.

These earrings have a sleek and sexy vibe - and will make a great addition to any style of wardrobe. They can be worn with a variety of outfits - dressed up or down!

They measure approx. 2-1/2” in length and 3/8” in width, and will hang for a total length of 3” from the top of the yellow bronze ear wires. The earrings are signed on the back with my initials.

name: Copper Tribal Earrings with Dangling Lapis Lazuli Gemstones
description:
These earrings have sold, but a similar pair can be created exclusively for you. Please contact me if you are interested.

Handmade copper metalwork earrings featuring dangling blue lapis lazuli gemstones. These unique earrings have a modern, tribal feel. I designed the earring shapes, sawed them out of solid copper sheet, and then created a tribal pattern by stamping and hammering the metal. The copper was oxidized, buffed and polished to bring out the texture's detail. Stunning lapis lazuli gemstones were added to dangle from the bottom. These stones are a gorgeous shade of blue and have natural pyrite inclusions.

The earrings measure 2-1/2" in length and 1-1/8" in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of approx 2-3/4" from the top of the niobium (hypoallergenic) ear wires. They are signed on the back with my initials.

name: Contemporary Copper Cuff Bracelet with Organic Roller Printed Texture
description:
This roller printed copper cuff has a modern, organic and contemporary appeal.

I created the texture in this cuff by putting the metal thru a steel rolling mill. After rolling the metal, I sawed the cuff out of solid copper sheet and created wavy edges into the metal for an organic effect. The edges were hand filed and sanded until smooth - to ensure a comfortable wear against the skin. The metal was oxidized, buffed, polished and sealed with a coat of wax to help preserve the finish.

Due to the unique texture - this cuff is a one-of-a-kind piece. It has an sleek modern style - and can be worn with a variety of outfits and styles.

The cuff measures 1-5/8” in width and 6” in length, along with a 1-1/4” opening in the back - for a total circumference of 7-1/4". This bracelet was hand forged from sturdy 20 gauge solid copper sheet, but is malleable enough to conform to your individual wrist. It should fit an average wrist that measures between 6-7 inches.

name: Sterling Silver Tribal Earrings with Black Onyx Gemstones and Unique Hand Stamped Design
description:
Handcrafted sterling silver earrings with a unique, tribal and exotic vibe. I designed the earring shapes; sawed them out of solid sterling silver sheet; and then hammered and stamped the silver to create a tribal texture. The metal was given a charcoal patina, and then buffed and polished to bring out the detail. Black onyx gemstones were added to complete the modern look. The tiny onyx stones are faceted - which adds a touch of sparkle and shine.

These earrings are very versatile and can be worn with a variety of outfits – dressed up or down! They would look great with a black dress, your favorite jeans – or just about anything. They will make a bold, unique and artsy statement.

They measure 2-1/8” in length and 1-1/4” in width (at the widest point) and will hang for a total length of 2-1/2” from the top of the sterling silver ear wires. The earrings are signed on the back with my initials and the sterling stamp.

name: Hand Forged Sculptural Copper Earrings - Modern Metalwork Jewelry
description:
Hand forged copper earrings with a bold, modern and contemporary aesthetic. I created these earrings out of solid copper sheet. I designed the modern shapes, sawed them out and then hammered and hand forged the metal for depth, texture and a sculptural effect. The copper was oxidized, buffed and polished for an earthy, antiqued finish - and to bring out the warm glow of the metal.

These earrings are versatile and could be worn with anything - dressed up or down! They have a bold and contemporary aesthetic and will make quite an artsy statement.

They measure approx. 2-1/8” in length and 1-3/4” in width, and will hang for a total length of approx. 2-3/4" from the top of the ear wires. They are shown with my hand forged copper ear wires - but if you prefer niobium (hypoallergenic) ear wires, just chose that option upon purchasing and I will switch the wires to niobium prior to sending. The earrings are signed on the back with my initials.

name: Sterling Silver Tribal Shield Earrings with Hammered Organic Texture
description:
These earrings have sold, but a similar pair can be created exclusively for you. Please contact me if you are interested.

These handmade tribal shield earrings have a sleek, modern and organic vibe. Due to their minimalist and simplistic feel, they can be worn with a variety of outfits and styles. They feature a modern tribal shield shape along with a rich organic texture. I drew the shapes, sawed them out of solid sterling silver sheet, and then deeply hammered them to create the rich, primal texture. The metal was given a charcoal patina and then buffed and polished to bring out the fabulous detail. 

The earrings measure 1-7/8” in length and 1” in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of approx. 2-1/4” from the top of the sterling silver ear wires. The earrings are signed on the back with my initials and the sterling stamp.

name: Long Tribal Spear Earrings with Natural Turquoise - Bold Exotic Tribal Jewelry
description:
Stacks of earthy turquoise were combined with hand fabricated brass spears to create these exotic, tribal earrings.

I created the shapes out of solid gold brass, and then hammered them for an earthy, organic texture. The metal was oxidized, buffed and polished for an antiqued finish. Gorgeous stacks of earthy turquoise were added to complete the tribal look. This turquoise has a lovely blue-green hue, along with a natural matrix of brown veining.

The earrings measure 2-7/8" in length and 3/4" in width (at widest point) and will hang for a total length of approx. 3-5/8" from the top of my hand forged brass ear wires. They are signed on the back with my initials.

These earrings have an exotic and "Old World" type of feel - and will make a bold statement!

name: Exotic Tribal Spear Earrings with African Glass Beads
description:
These earrings have sold, but a similar pair can be created exclusively for you. Please contact me if you are interested.

These handmade earrings have an earthy, primitive and ancient "Old World" vibe - and will make a bold and exotic statement!!They feature hand fabricated, African inspired brass spears combined with hand painted African glass beads. I drew the spear shapes, sawed them out of solid gold brass sheet, and then stamped a primitive tribal pattern into the metal. The brass was oxidized to give it an antiqued "Old World" finish. African glass and brown wood beads were added to complete the bohemian, tribal look. These glass beads have a lovely hand painted pattern with earthy tones of blue, brown and some "hints" of green.

The earrings measure 3” in length and 1-1/4” in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of approx. 3-1/4” from the top of the yellow bronze ear wires. The earrings are signed on the back with my initials.

name: Egyptian Inspired Mixed Metal Dangle Earrings with Sterling Silver and Copper
description:
These unique mixed metal earrings have an "Old World" and ancient, primal vibe. I designed the shapes and then sawed them out of solid copper sheet with a jeweler's saw. The metal was hammered, stamped and domed to create a sculptural texture, and then oxidized to bring out the detail. Abstract twists of sterling silver wire were added for an added touch of interest and detail. Rustic, African copper beads and sterling silver Bali beads were added to complete the primal look.

The earrings measure 2-1/4” in length and 3/4” in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of approx. 2-7/8”  from the top of the sterling silver ear wires.

name: Handmade Gold Brass Triangle Earrings with Black Onyx Gemstones
description:
These earrings have sold, but a similar pair can be created exclusively for you. Please contact me if you are interested.

Geometric jewelry is really in vogue right now - so these handmade earrings will make a hip, trendy statement! They feature hand fabricated gold brass triangles along with black onyx gemstones. I created the triangular shapes out of solid gold brass sheet and then hammered them to create an organic, earthy texture. The metal was lightly oxidized to bring out the rich detail. Gorgeous black onyx stones were added to complete the modern, geometric look. These natural onyx stones have a great triangular shape and an earthy matte finish.

They measure 2-1/2” in length and 1-1/4” in width (at the widest point), and will hang for a total length of approx. 2-7/8" from the top of the yellow bronze ear wires. The earrings are signed on the back with my initials.
